    {"Narrator": """The evening air in Millbrook, Connecticut carries the last warmth of summer, mixing with the musty scent of cardboard boxes and forgotten sheet music. Maya Chen stands in the doorway of her father's music school - now her music school - surrounded by the ghosts of her past..."""},
