    {"Narrator": """The room falls silent. Maya Chen and Jack Sullivan lock eyes across the conference table, the tension crackling between them like a faulty Wi-Fi connection."""},
    {"Editor": """Actually... this is perfect. This is exactly what we need!"""},
    {"Maya": """What?"""},
    {"Jack": """Excuse me?"""},
    {"Editor": """The chemistry, the conflict, the completely opposing worldviews! You two are going to co-write a series together. 'Love in the Digital Age: A Dialogue Between the Heart and the Algorithm.'"""},
