    {"Narrator": """The editor leans back, watching the sparks fly with barely contained glee."""},
    {"Editor": """Here's the deal. One year. Twelve articles. Each month you'll explore a different aspect of modern love. Dating apps, social media's impact on relationships, digital vs. traditional courtship... And here's the kicker – you'll have to experience everything you write about. Together."""},
    {"Jack": """This is absurd. I write about digital detox and authentic living. I can't collaborate with someone who thinks love can be reduced to an algorithm!"""},
    {"Maya": """For once we agree on something. I deal in facts and data, not nostalgic fantasies about the "good old days" that never actually existed."""},
    {"Editor": """Your first assignment starts today. You'll profile each other's digital presence – social media, online articles, dating profiles, all of it. I want to see drafts by Friday."""},
