    {"Editor": """Perfect! This is exactly the energy I want in the series. Raw, honest, controversial... Meet in the lobby at 3 PM to start your research. And remember – everything that happens is potential content."""},
    {"Narrator": """As they storm out of the conference room in opposite directions, neither notices the editor's satisfied smirk. Sometimes the best stories write themselves – they just need a little push in the right direction..."""},
    {"Narrator": """The lobby of TechCrunch's San Francisco office is a careful blend of industrial chic and Silicon Valley modernism. At precisely 2:57 PM, Maya claims the corner couch, opens her laptop, and starts aggressively typing."""},
    {"Jack": """You're actually here early. Let me guess - your calendar app told you to arrive precisely 180 seconds before the meeting to optimize your productivity?"""},
    {"Maya": """I've already scraped your entire digital footprint. Did you know you've used the phrase 'soul-crushing digital dystopia' seventeen times in your articles this year alone?"""},
