{"Lucia": """You underestimate how well Florence guards its traditions."""},
{"Piero": """And you underestimate how bright a light can shine, even through the thickest walls of custom."""},
{"Narrator": """Two weeks have passed. The workshop hums with activity as Lucia works at the design table, surrounded by geometric calculations and sketches. Lorenzo cuts glass at the far table while Giovanni entertains an unexpected visitor."""},
{"Marco": """The guild masters are concerned, Giovanni. Three months without a workshop inspection is unprecedented."""},
{"Giovanni": """The Medici commission requires absolute concentration, Marco. Surely the guild understands."""},
{"Marco": """What we understand is that your recent works show marked changes in style. Some would say improvements."""},
{"Lorenzo": """Our father's skill only grows with experience."""},
